abstract: Quarterback Tim Tebow is expected to sign one-year contract with Philadelphia Eagles.
lead_paragraph: Tebow was expected to sign a one-year contract with the Philadelphia Eagles on Monday, according to several news media reports citing people who requested anonymity.

headline.main: Reports Say Tim Tebow Will Return to the N.F.L.
headline.print_headline: Reports Say Tebow Will Return to the N.F.L.
